-- Bashneft seeks green light to sell up to 45 mln shares in London
-- 
-- Tue Jul 08, 2014 12:02PM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, July 8 (Reuters) - Russian oil producer Bashneft <BANE.MM> said on Tuesday it was seeking approval from the central bank to issue up to 45 million shares in a London listing, up from 37 million planned before. [ID:nL6N0PF16M]

Bashneft earlier said it could place between $1 billion and $2 billion worth of shares in London as early as September. [ID:nL6N0ON1IR]